title: BRIEF-HCA Healthcare Says About 29 Pct Of Qtrly Admission Growth Was Flu-Related
text:
May 1, 2018 / 4:32 PM / Updated 17 minutes ago BRIEF-HCA Healthcare Says About 29 Pct Of Qtrly Admission Growth Was Flu-Related Reuters Staff 1 Min Read

* HCA HEALTHCARE PRESIDENT SAMUEL HAZEN SAYS ABOUT 29 PERCENT OF QTRLY ADMISSION GROWTH WAS FLU-RELATED - CONF CALL
